price: ¿Acaso surgieron de la nada o son ellos sus propios creadores?
arabic: أَمۡ خُلِقُواْ مِنۡ غَيۡرِ شَيۡءٍ أَمۡ هُمُ ٱلۡخَٰلِقُونَ
footnotes: surgieron de la nada: Sin Creador que los creara.

version.title: Spanish Translation - Isa Garcia
version.description: Translation of the Quran meanings into Spanish by Muhammad Isa Garcia - Printed in 1433 H.

meta.transliteration: am khuliqū min ghayri shayin am humu al-khāliqūna
